Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.block.filtering

Class Summary
Filter AApplies the XPath expression to the incoming value and only those are forwarded which maches it.
FilterCollection Filter the elements of the collection via the XPath expression and return a filtered collection.
FilterMapByKey Filter the keys of the map via the XPath expression and return a map with only those elements where the filter matched the key.
FilterMapByValue Filter the values of the map via the XPath expression and return a map with only those elements where the filter matched the value.
